Assessment Criteria

Client Engagement: Effectiveness in identifying and communicating with the client.

Problem Analysis: Depth and clarity in understanding the problem.

Solution Design: Creativity, practicality, and technical soundness of the proposed solution.

Analysis and Ethical Consideration: Thoroughness in analyzing the design and considering its broader implications.

Presentation and Communication Skills: Clarity and professionalism in all forms of communication.

Collaboration and Teamwork: Ability to work effectively as a team.
